thread.title_full: Uitlaat Winkel Beoordeeld door Henrique Mauricio

author: Henrique Mauricio
title: Henrique Mauricio
text:
I called before ordering to make sure the parts were compatible, the person that answered the call was very nice and comprehensive. The order came with little to no protection and the box a little damaged. But inside was only metal and rubbers.
Was a simple order, and a fast shipping
